### Dashboard page
GET http://localhost:3000/entries

### Create a journal entry
POST http://localhost:3000/entries/new
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

title=Reading+Notes&body=This+body+is+long+enough+to+be+valid.&tag=reading

### Toggle entry 1
POST http://localhost:3000/entries/1/toggle

### Search entries
GET http://localhost:3000/entries/search?q=reading

### Filter completed entries
GET http://localhost:3000/entries/filter?status=completed
